## Question 9
*Write a program that checks the input for zero and multiples of 10 and says "Zero!" or "Multiple of ten" accordingly.*

```cpp
#include <iostream>
int main(int argc, char* argv[]) {
  std::cout << "Please enter a number:\n";
  int num;
  std::cin >> num;
  if (num == 0)
    std::cout << "Zero!";
  else if (num%10 == 0)
    std::cout << "Multiple of 10!";
  std::cout << "\n";
}
```

